{% comment %}
  The Y Section Snippet
  
  Renders the "WHAT'S YOUR Y?" section content.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="the-y-section" style="background-image: url('{{ 'bg_blue.jpg' | asset_url }}');">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="the-y-content">
      
      <!-- Top Content Grid -->
      <div class="the-y-grid">

        <!-- Left Side -->
        <div class="the-y-vitruvian">

          <div class="the-y-title">
            <img src="{{ 'title_1.png' | asset_url }}" alt="What's Your Y?" class="the-y-heading-image" width="300" height="100">
          </div>

          <div class="vitruvian-container">
            <div class="vitruvian-man">
              <img src="{{ 'v_man_logo.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Vitruvian Man" class="vitruvian-image" width="300" height="300">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side -->
        <div class="the-right-side">
          
          <div class="the-y-bullets">
            <div class="bullet-point">
              <div class="bullet-icon"></div>
              <p>Your Y chromosome produces testosterone at levels that define what it is to be a man.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bullet-point">
              <div class="bullet-icon"></div>
              <p>Age, stress and other variables can cause these levels to nosedive and deplete your energy and masculinity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bullet-point">
              <div class="bullet-icon"></div>
              <p>Big Richard Energy: The Y-PLEX helps boost your testosterone levels naturally so you can perform better: <span class="performance-highlight"><span class="red-bullet">•</span> PHYSICALLY <span class="red-bullet">•</span> MENTALLY <span class="red-bullet">•</span> SEXUALLY</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="the-y-lifestyle">
            <div class="lifestyle-images">
               <div class="lifestyle-image">
                 <img src="{{ 'v_image_1.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Baseball Field" class="lifestyle-img" width="400" height="200">
               </div>
              <div class="lifestyle-image">
                <div class="lifestyle-image">
                  <img src="{{ 'v_image_2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Baseball Field" class="lifestyle-img" width="400" height="200">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="the-y-tagline">
              <img src="{{ 'title_2.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Your Y Is Everything" class="the-y-tagline-image" width="400" height="80">
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.the-y-section {
  padding: 60px 0;
  color: white;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-size: cover;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

{% comment %} .the-y-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: 
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(220, 32, 13, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
  z-index: 1;
} {% endcomment %}

.the-y-section .container {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

.the-y-content {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Main Title */
.the-y-title {
  text-align: center;
}

.the-y-heading-image {
  max-width: 90%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Top Grid Layout */
.the-y-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: end;
}

/* Bullet Points */
.the-right-side {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 30px;
}

.the-y-bullets {
}

.bullet-point {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 15px;
}

.bullet-icon {
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  background: #dc200d;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.bullet-point p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #ffffff;
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.performance-highlight {
  color: #ffffff;
  font-weight: bold;
  display: block;
  line-height: 1;
}

.red-bullet {
  color: #dc200d;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

/* Vitruvian Man */
.the-y-vitruvian {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.vitruvian-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.vitruvian-man {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.vitruvian-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: contain;
  {% comment %} max-width: 300px; {% endcomment %}
  {% comment %} max-height: 300px; {% endcomment %}
}

.y-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  font-size: 4rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: #dc200d;
  z-index: 10;
  font-family: 'DIN Condensed', 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
}

.vitruvian-labels {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.label {
  position: absolute;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-family: 'DIN Condensed', 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
}

.label-mental {
  top: 10px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.label-masculinity {
  top: 50%;
  left: 10px;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
}

.label-physical {
  top: 50%;
  right: 10px;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
}

.label-sexual {
  bottom: 10px;
  right: 20px;
}

/* Lifestyle Section */
.the-y-lifestyle {
  text-align: center;
}

.lifestyle-images {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.lifestyle-image {
  position: relative;
}

.image-placeholder {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border: 2px solid #dc200d;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: #ffffff;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.lifestyle-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 2px solid #dc200d;
}

.the-y-tagline-image {
  max-width: 90%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Responsive design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .the-y-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  
  .the-y-heading-image {
    max-width: 90%;
  }
  
  .the-y-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  
  .y-overlay {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }
  
  .lifestyle-images {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .the-y-tagline-image {
    max-width: 90%;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .the-y-section {
    padding: 25px 0;
  }

  .the-y-heading-image {
    max-width: 85%;
  }
  
  .the-y-bullets {
    padding: 0px 20px;
  }

  .bullet-point p {
    line-height: 2;
  }
  
  .y-overlay {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .the-y-lifestyle {
    padding: 0 25px;
  }
  
}
</style>
